page.title: 11A SCHOOL DAY IN KEELBY
page.content: On a school day I go downstairs to have my cup of tea and my breakfast (Special K or Coco pops.)My sister goes to school then.She has to walk to the bus stop with her friend,then she gets on the school bus.She has to go by bus as her school isnot in Keelby but in Healing.I shall go there when I am 11.After she's gone to school and I've finished my breakfast I clean my teeth.Then I get my school basket ready and go to school.To get to my school I have to walk to the top of our road,cross over,walk down Wivell Drive and the school is across the playing field.
